Package de.griefed.serverpackcreator.i18n Description

i18n i.e. Localization, of ServerPackCreator.

Note from Griefed: I hate i18n. It is a headache-inducing, tedious, slow, time-consuming chore, especially if you have to fight or work with file-encoding.
